Europe started to fall apart.

00:47:13.620 --> 00:47:15.530 align:middle line:84%
Heck, we had our
S & P downgraded

00:47:15.530 --> 00:47:16.650 align:middle line:90%
in the United States.

00:47:16.650 --> 00:47:18.840 align:middle line:84%
And there was a real
crisis going on.

00:47:18.840 --> 00:47:20.670 align:middle line:84%
So that-- I think
it was at that point

00:47:20.670 --> 00:47:23.290 align:middle line:84%
where the central banks of
the world realized, holy cow.

00:47:23.290 --> 00:47:25.790 align:middle line:84%
All that stuff from '08, all
