exportation inflation

00:48:14.510 --> 00:48:16.000 align:middle line:90%
around the world.

00:48:16.000 --> 00:48:21.680 align:middle line:84%
So not just the Arab Spring, but
it's starting to go everywhere.

00:48:21.680 --> 00:48:23.060 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It is
a global economy.

